Spark Streaming's Kinesis libraries not found in class path. Try one of the following.

  1. Include the Streaming's Kinesis library and its dependencies with in the
     spark-submit command as

     $ bin/spark-submit --packages org.apache.spark:spark-streaming-kinesis-asl:3.2.1 ...

  2. Download the JAR of the artifact from Maven Central http://search.maven.org/,
     Group Id = org.apache.spark, Artifact Id = spark-streaming-kinesis-asl-assembly, Version = 3.2.1.
     Then, include the jar in the spark-submit command as

     $ bin/spark-submit --jars <spark-streaming-kinesis-asl-assembly.jar> ...

-----------------------------
The following submit worked:
spark-submit --master local[2] --packages org.apache.spark:spark-streaming-kinesis-asl_2.12:3.1.3\
    spark-example/b_spark_streaming_example.py


